latestPosts.caption:
A year of endless scrolling through Instagram and Pinterest, watching weddings, saving ideas, and dreaming of our own. 

It has been a MAD MAD ride!

They say it all goes by in the blink of an eye, and they are absolutely right. A dream we would relive every single day if we could—our wedding is now yours to see. 

And to quote Monica Geller: ‘I’ll never be a bride again. Now I’m just someone’s wife.’ 😭
.
.
